    },
    {
      "character": "",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "哗啦啦……"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "closemouth",
      "text": "第2次。……今天也很壮观啊。真的，高潮时的表情太色了，最棒了。"
